            <h2>Comments</h2>
            <p>In-line comments are made with <code>--</code> and block comments with <code>&lbrace;- -&rbrace;</code>: </p>
<CodeBlock language="Haskell" highlight_as="haskell"><Fragment slot="code-example">-- inline
commentHere = False &lbrace;
- block commentHere = True -&rbrace; 
